- cs.CG (Computational Geometry): The paper involves reparameterizing curves and constructing surfaces, which are common topics in computational geometry. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves solving algebraic equations, which is a common topic in control theory and systems engineering. 
- cs.CA (Computational Algebra): The paper involves solving algebraic equations, which is a common topic in computational algebra. 
- cs.GM (Geometric Modeling): The paper deals with constructing surfaces bounded by curves, which is a common topic in geometric modeling.
